      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>This is your last chance to buy this book! It's a copy of the first edition and that's the only one left. You can't find it anywhere else! Actually, Symbol Scholar Kahlua wanted to buy this book but he was sent to Wasteland Battlefield on an urgent mission. That's why you were lucky enough to find it…….<FONT color=#7e12d2>(April starts to use her selling skills on you.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
