      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-c" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Tryan's Territory?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>……You mean you don't want to buy this one but its sequel? I don't have it right now.<BR>Actually, this book was found in <FONT color=#a82424>Tryan's Territory</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
