      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>You must be thinking whether you should risk your life by going to Tryan's Territory just for one book. I've thought about it and I think I can make this special request, to you and only you <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
