      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Could it be that a Child appeared out of nowhere one day and killed Daidalos and his family and took over the maze like what happened to the Lazuli kingdom? If it's a book that contains important information like that, Tryan could have burnt it......</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
